{"tid":1072233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國科學家創全球第一款「毒蜘蛛辣醬」","createTime":"2019-03-22T01:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T04:47:53.000Z","uid":13468,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bdcc473608b8276b2c9dc774ab15950e4628d197","tid":1072233,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:40:26.000Z","msg":"敢吃嗎？ 英國科學家創全球第一款「毒蜘蛛辣醬」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php1UY7T2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php1UY7T2.jpg&h=6683fa2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國一名科學家日前宣布，創造了世上第一款「毒蜘蛛辣醬」，該辣醬是在萃取蜘蛛毒液後調製而成，吃進去對人體無害，恰到好處的辣度加上特殊的多層次口感，讓食客能安全享受到「品嘗猛毒」的奇特進食體驗。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，英國藥物研究公司Venomtech創辦人兼科學家崔姆（Steve Trim）表示，在得知蜘蛛毒液對人體造成的刺激感和辣椒的原理相同的資訊後，他們使用「千里達老虎尾蜘蛛」的毒液，萃取其中對人體無害的成分，混合辣椒和其他香料，最終成功完成第一批使用300隻蜘蛛毒液製成的48罐辣醬，開賣後目前已銷售一空。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，食客回饋分成2類，對於特別愛辣的人而言，他們覺得辣醬沒有想像中嗆辣；對於不太吃辣的人而言，他們卻覺得口味非常辣。崔姆的團隊認為成果不錯，辣度剛好介於中間值。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，由於辣醬詢問度很高，崔姆和他的團隊已開始研發新的沾醬，未來除了口味更溫和的「毒美乃滋」外，還打算推出蜘蛛辣醬乳酪麵包，盼能在年內上市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2734654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2734654&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=6db993f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2734654&h=89e7808f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2734654</a>"},{"pid":"94da7709c18e56d0651808524ac9ab57a8bcf0b9","tid":1072233,"uid":95096,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:42:37.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體對人體無害"},{"pid":"6128287ee500128a2e99df10ee72a5e1b9f946af","tid":1072233,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"班蜘蛛好慘"},{"pid":"170f9069a82ed5365a0a39fbe06bd239713b5441","tid":1072233,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f74466b321cc49af878920caeb3d509d5eab9b","tid":1072233,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:46:20.000Z","msg":"英國研究 中國製造"},{"pid":"c1611fa5c18dab664a793ef110e7f857d1910b27","tid":1072233,"uid":85461,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"英國研究 中國製造 台灣報導 <br />\n齊曬!"},{"pid":"0ed709c5986a5549a80d40b9ac3afec924ac15c8","tid":1072233,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"食完變毒魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fce714894848e9d82e82fde6c3d1c80db756ee","tid":1072233,"uid":13468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/55382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F55382.jpg&h=7bbece03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53c2d1a56d24e100dfdfed23bfc105f83d655ef7","tid":1072233,"uid":122233,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">報導指出，食客回饋分成2類，對於特別愛辣的人而言，他們覺得辣醬沒有想像中嗆辣；對於不太吃辣的人而言，他們卻覺得口味非常辣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"15963a8f6d9e06245757d7fc8b7b206477da0169","tid":1072233,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:53:28.000Z","msg":"啲味咪又係來自辣椒同香料 有咩咁特別？"},{"pid":"a70c2f4e136d3fc8eb601b73fd40bd26eb7d3fdd","tid":1072233,"uid":212535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15963a8f6d9e06245757d7fc8b7b206477da0169","tid":1072233,"uid":201604,"lik